(42, 'string', 'content_en', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<h3>These photos give you a snapshot of our natural learning environments.</h3>\r\n<p>All classrooms and outdoor learning areas are large and spacious and exceed the regulated space requirements allowing children quiet spaces to play as well as opportunities for social engagement.</p>', NULL, '2022-08-18 18:31:56'),
