(51, 'string', 'Second_content', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Children benefit from a wide variety of fun play-based activities, equipment and craft.</p>\r\n<p>All playgroups are held in the community hall in each locality in the mornings. The cost of attending a playgroup session is $2.00 per child (babies under 1 year free) and caters for families with children 0-6 years. Mums, dads, grandparents and carers are all welcome to attend. <br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Our 2024 Calendar is attached below.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong> <br />For additional information please phone the Pre School on <a title=\"Gloucester Pre School Phone\" href=\"tel:+61265581643\">02 65581643</a></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><a title=\"Playgroup Calendar 2024\" href=\"uploads/Playgroup Calendar 2024.pdf\">Playgroup Calendar 2024</a></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2024-01-30 14:42:26'),
