(41, 'string', 'content_en', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<h4>Management Committee&nbsp;</h4>\r\n<p>Gloucester Preschool Incorporated is managed by a committee of volunteer parents. This enables the service to remain a non-profit organisation.</p>\r\n<p>Management positions are declared vacant at the Annual General Meeting each year and all parents are welcome to stand for positions and to attend meetings.</p>\r\n<p>The Committee meets monthly to ensure that the service continues to operate legally, ethically and to a high standard of practice.</p>', NULL, '2022-08-22 10:05:48'),
