(40, 'string', 'content_en', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Long Day Care (LDC) Enrollment</strong></p>\r\n<p>Gloucester Preschool is able to offer Long Day Care enrollments. Long day Care days are available to children under the age of 6 and operates 8am to 5:15pm, Monday to Friday for 50 weeks per year. The Government\'s&nbsp;new Child Care Subsidy package will determine the fee per day for LDC enrollments.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Preschool&nbsp;Enrollment</strong></p>\r\n<p>Our Preschool program is available to children 3 years to school age and operates&nbsp;8:15am - 3:45pm during term time. We are funded by the NSW Government under their Early Childhood Education Program. Two days of free preschool are available for children 3 to 5 years of age. There is a daily charge of $5 to cover the cost of meals. You will not be charged fees for school holidays, but can book into our vacation care program for a small daily fee.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Fee Information</strong></p>\r\n<p>Preschool fees and the Long Day Care fees will be invoiced two weeks in advance as per the Australian Governments&nbsp;New Child&nbsp;Care Package.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Two weeks&rsquo; notice should be given if your child is leaving Pre-school.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>A copy of the&nbsp;fees policy is located in the Parent Login in section under policies</p>\r\n<p>National Law and Regulations - link attached below to view&nbsp;the National laws and regulations that govern our service</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"National Law and Regulations\" href=\"https://legislation.nsw.gov.au/view/html/inforce/current/sl-2011-0653\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">National Law and Regulations</a></p>', NULL, '2022-09-30 09:02:21'),
