(33, 'string', 'content_en', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<h2>Gloucester Pre School and Early Years Learning Centre is a non-profit community-based organisation, established in 1972.&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p>We operate the following services:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Pre School for children 3 to 5 years of age</li>\r\n<li>Long Day Care for children 0 to 5 years of age</li>\r\n<li>Support Mobile Playgroup in regional towns</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>The service is assessed through the National Quality Standards and is rated as Exceeding&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Our service has been recognised for its ongoing commitment to leading the profession through the following awards.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2018 Winner of the National PlaySafe Design Awards for the Education &amp; Care Services</p>\r\n<p>2022 Winner of the National Hesta Leadership Award for Early Childhood education &amp; Care Services&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The service is run by a parent management committee and we value parents&rsquo; contributions and support parenting with information, advice, resources and the opportunity to establish new networks.</p>', NULL, '2023-07-20 16:41:26'),
(61, 'string', 'page', NULL, NULL, NULL, '49', NULL, '2022-08-10 13:58:38'),
(38, 'string', 'design_id', NULL, NULL, NULL, '10', NULL, '2022-08-05 14:07:13'),
(38, 'string', 'searchable', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', NULL, '2022-08-05 14:07:13'),
(38, 'string', 'content_en', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Learning environments are designed to support children\'s learning and social connections. We have four classrooms and two large outdoor learning areas.</p>\r\n<p>The service has a strong sustainability vision and we support a low carbon footprint and teach children to play in a landscape that support biodiversity.</p>', NULL, '2022-08-05 14:07:13'),
