(68, 'string', 'Second_content', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Long Day Care for Pre School Aged Children</strong></p>\r\n<p>Families requiring longer hours of education and care for preschool-aged children can use our long day care facilities. These children will experience the preschool program from 8.15 am to 3.45 pm. They have a quieter session during the extended hours often family grouping with younger children. This provides a more homely structure where children have the opportunities for quieter play, extended story reading, songs and conversations with educators.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Long Day Care for children 0 to 3 years of age see Early Years Learning Centre Information</strong></p>', NULL, '2022-09-06 12:35:30'),
